g.text: submits transaction containing a double hash of the data, and data to trusted Full Node
submits the transaction to a single authority for inclusion
submits a block to the rest of the authority set
after two rounds of 2f+1, transaction is finalized
the contacted authority returns a finality proof
contacts shard members using a seed from the finality proof threshold signature, transaction digest, and data hash
after processing the data into embeddings, encoders commit an encrypted embedding to the rest of the shard members
download encrypted embedding of other shard members, and when safe, reveal the encryption key (commit reveal)
after evaluating the decrypted embeddings, against their respective probe models, final scores are broadcast to the rest of the shard
the final embeddings and corresponding scores are returned
full node notifies encoders that they have received the endorsement to stop timeouts
the endorsement, or quorum of scores, is returned to the authority set for claiming the winnings
finality proof is submitted back to the encoder who submitted
notify all shard members of finality to stop any timeouts
